              </div>

              <p>ACM-W India proudly celebrates the remarkable achievements of young women representing India at prestigious international informatics olympiads in 2026. Their dedication, excellence, and perseverance continue to inspire the next generation of women in computing.</p>

              <h3 style="color: #043b87;">🇮🇳 India at the European Girls’ Olympiad in Informatics (EGOI-2026)</h3>
              <p>Held in Cesenatico, Italy (12–18 May 2026), the Indian team showcased exceptional talent and brought pride to the nation.</p>
              <p><strong>👏 Congratulations to:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>🥇 <strong>Swasti Vitthal Patil</strong> – Gold Medal (India’s first-ever Gold Medal at EGOI)</li>
                <li>🥈 <strong>Mansi Sane</strong> – Silver Medal</li>
                <li>🥉 <strong>Diya Sathishdev</strong> – Bronze Medal</li>
                <li>🎖️ <strong>Lyra Floyd Gonsalves</strong> – Honourable Mention</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p>Sonia Garcha led the Indian contingent from CSpathshala, who is also a committee member at large - ACM-W India, an educator and computing mentor dedicated to promoting computational thinking and nurturing young talent in informatics and computer science education across India.</p>
              
              <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;margin:20px 0;">

              <h3 style="color: #043b87;">🌎 Asia-Pacific Informatics Olympiad (APIO-2026)</h3>
              <p>India also achieved remarkable success at APIO-2026 with:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>🥇 <strong>Samik Goyal</strong> – Gold Medal</li>
                <li>🥉 <strong>Naman Singh</strong>, <strong>Mohammad Farhat</strong>, <strong>Arjun Tyagi</strong>, <strong>Avighna Chhatrapati</strong> – Bronze Medals</li>
              </ul>

              <p>These achievements reflect the growing strength of India’s young computing talent and the importance of creating inclusive opportunities for students in technology and problem-solving.</p>
              
